sequenceDiagram
    actor PB as Patient Browser
    participant NX as Next.js (Patient Portal)
    participant NE as NestJS API
    participant ML as FastAPI ML Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant WS as Patient Browser (WS)

    PB->>NX: Drop image in upload zone
    NX->>NE: POST /cases (multipart, Patient JWT)\nscope=PATIENT
    activate NE
    NE->>NE: Validate JWT → role=PATIENT\nExtract userId, scope=PATIENT
    NE->>NE: Store file to\nuploads/patients/{userId}/{caseId}/
    NE->>ML: POST /predict {imagePath}
    activate ML
    ML->>ML: Hash filename → select mock_results.json entry\nAdd Gaussian noise (σ=0.02)\nSleep 1.5–3s (mock latency)
    ML-->>NE: PredictionResult {predictedSubtype, confidence,\nprobs[4], attentionMap, modelVersion}
    deactivate ML
    NE->>DB: INSERT Case {scope=PATIENT, userId,\nstoredLocally=true, predictedSubtype, confidence}
    DB-->>NE: Case saved
    NE-->>NX: 201 CaseSummary {id, predictedSubtype, confidence, status=PENDING}
    deactivate NE
    NX-->>PB: Render plain-language result\n+ confidence badge (High/Medium/Low)\n+ non-dismissable disclaimer

    Note over PB,DB: NO FL round triggered — Patient uploads stay in Patient Space

    alt confidence = Low
        PB->>PB: Show ⚠ "Please consult a specialist" warning
    end

    PB->>WS: Click "Ask AI about this"
    WS-->>PB: Navigate to chat with caseId query param
